oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Red clover: a promising pasture legume for Ireland.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Weldon, B.A.
O'Kiely, P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Pasture and forage crops
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This experiment quantified the impacts of cultivar, companion grass, harvest schedule and nitrogen fertiliser on crop yield in the sixth year after establishment, and compared these to grass receiving inorganic N fertiliser.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Weldon, B.A. and O'Kiely, P. (2011) Red clover: a promising pasture legume for Ireland. In: Summary of Papers Presented at the Agricultural Research Forum, Teagasc, Tullamore.
